{
  "id": "adv_card_rui_53_01",
  "title": "天動瑠依",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――十一月十一日　朝",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "これはネギ塩カルビ味、こっちはサルミアッキ味……\nふふ、美味しそうなグミがこんなに沢山……！",
      "startTime": 9.3,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9933.3333333,
          "startTime": 19.2333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "やはり皆さん、大好きなグミを用意していたんですね\nこれ、私からです。味が被っていないといいのですが",
      "startTime": 18.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "本当？　ありがとう、沙季。被りは気にしないで\nグミはいくつあってもいいもの。同じ味でも大歓迎よ",
      "startTime": 28.4478900273,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "あら？　でも、そっちに持ってるのは何かしら？\n魚の干物みたいだけど。真空パック……？",
      "startTime": 37.8812233607,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "これは一応、被ってしまった時のために用意していた物\nですね。体に良くて、私は好きなんですが……",
      "startTime": 46.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "サブのプランまで用意しているなんて、さすがね\n……ねぇ、良ければそれも食べてみていいかしら？",
      "startTime": 56.0584114074,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_plasticbag-02.m4a",
          "delay": 10674.921925899995,
          "startTime": 66.7333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんです。ただ、その、これは『くさや』ですので\nもしかしたら匂いが……ってここで開けるんですか！？",
      "startTime": 65.4666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_microwave-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5617.456882800014,
          "startTime": 71.0841235495
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_microwave-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7433.333333300013,
          "startTime": 72.9
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_microwave-03.m4a",
          "delay": 7666.666666600008,
          "startTime": 73.1333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 15850.784365200014,
          "startTime": 81.3174510319
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "うん、電子レンジでいい感じに温まったわね。においも\n気になるほどじゃないし。はむ……ん～、味もいいわ",
      "startTime": 78.7174510319,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "本当ですか！？　良かった、用意した甲斐がありました\n疲労回復にいいので、瑠依さんに合うと思ったんです",
      "startTime": 93.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "昔からクレームが凄いので、もう寮では食べないように\nしていたくらいなんですが、気に入ってもらえるなんて",
      "startTime": 100.9333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 12065.3652508,
          "startTime": 112.9986985841
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、もっと歯ごたえがあった方が、より美味しいわね\nそうだ、このサルミアッキのグミを一緒に食べれば……",
      "startTime": 110.3986985841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "うん、やっぱり、より美味しくなったわ！\nあとは、ソース味のグミで味を整えたいわね",
      "startTime": 119.1986985841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "え、瑠依さん？　どんどんくさやが大変なことに……\nしかもソース味って、せめてお醤油では……！？",
      "startTime": 128.2333363851,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "こういうのは意外性があった方がいいのよ\nプリンの隠し味に、お醤油を垂らすって言うでしょ？",
      "startTime": 136.1024006206,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
          "delay": 12797.599379399997,
          "startTime": 148.9
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "それはウニの味にする方法では！？　冗談かと\n思ってましたが、もしや瑠依さんは、本当に味覚が……",
      "startTime": 144.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっとなんなのよこのにおい！！\nあんた達、事務所で何してんの！？",
      "startTime": 151.9802917161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "あ、莉央さん。今、沙季のおすすめの食べ物を\nより美味しくしようと研究しているところなんです",
      "startTime": 158.7136250494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "良ければ、莉央さんも一緒にどうですか？　これが現状\n最強の、くさやのサルミアッキとソースのグミ添えです",
      "startTime": 166.4802917161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "黒魔術でもやってんの！？\nいいから早く換気してちょうだい、お願いだから！！",
      "startTime": 173.8136250494,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}